Introduction

Dang Hong Hai is a Vietnamese trainee under Dongyo Entertainment. He is best known for participating in the show "The Voice Kids Vietnam" in 2016 and in the 2022 Korean survival show "Boys Planet" where he ranked 42nd place, unfortunately being eliminated on the show.

He was originally under Fantagio but ended his contract with the company and Dongyo Entertainment announced Dang Hong Hai under the company on October 26th, 2023.

Dang Hong Hai is a member of NEWKIES (DONGYO NEW ROOKIES, a pre-debut trainee group under Dongyo Entertainment. There debut date has not been confirmed.
